{"tid":1142558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（台狗醒覺）「不建議窮人生小孩」惹爭議","createTime":"2019-05-07T06:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T11:00:08.000Z","uid":160807,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed1bf7dbfd78e260b39e2780db4b0a40bfc07ea","tid":1142558,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"「窮真的不是藉口！」台灣機車族多，經常可見父母騎機車載幼兒出門，偶爾還會碰上3貼、4貼的狀況，雖然有人認為可以包容體諒，但也有人覺得此舉相當危險，其中擁有E罩杯火辣身材的網紅「T妹」就在臉書痛批，認為騎機車就不該載小孩，這是一種責任感，甚至直言「窮人就是不建議生小孩，除非你可以給小孩最基本生活品質」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1_HRe7J8_VunKRSt3p83uw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTIwMDtoPTY3NQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/0044ecdceecf1017dc41f2dd67016b40\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1_HRe7J8_VunKRSt3p83uw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTIwMDtoPTY3NQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2F0044ecdceecf1017dc41f2dd67016b40&h=643f745c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼T妹發文砲轟，認為不該騎機車載幼兒。（圖／T妹臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fbbyb0VcTzqc2AAs19FHwA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQzO2g9ODU1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/e2450be12d48285e82fca3bcd247db72\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Ffbbyb0VcTzqc2AAs19FHwA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQzO2g9ODU1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2Fe2450be12d48285e82fca3bcd247db72&h=512baddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nT妹（Tiffany Chen）在臉書直言，帶小孩騎機車結果出車禍，最後大人沒事，小孩卻重傷或死亡，類似的案例層出不窮，雖然有人可能會解釋，因為住偏遠地區，沒有大眾交通工具，只能騎車，但5歲以下幼兒不建議用機車載，這不但是許多學者同意的觀點，也是常識，「我不是說騎車不好，而是不應該載幼小的小孩，因為他們身體較軟、脆弱，如果發生意外甚至死亡，父母就是幫凶」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/B86M11BVrqpy5MhY_zUw.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU2O2g9ODc5/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/c31b8d2cefef5ace1039bb94f4230571\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FB86M11BVrqpy5MhY_zUw.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU2O2g9ODc5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2Fc31b8d2cefef5ace1039bb94f4230571&h=7088c0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nT妹痛心坦言，自己也窮過，20歲時就想生小孩，但當時沒有經濟能力給孩子安全生活，因此拖到至今才敢生，身邊的朋友也因為抱持對孩子的責任感，堅持生孩子就要養他及確保安全，最後過了適當的生育年齡還未生，「社會在進步，不是把方便、隨便、窮掛在嘴邊當理所當然」，直言「不要拿窮掛嘴邊」，呼籲若是經濟狀況不佳，就不建議生，何況有些人不是真正窮，只是貪圖方便才用機車載幼兒，最後痛批「我真的很看不起3貼或草菅人命的父母，完全不懂嚴重性與尊重生命」。<br />\n<br />\n▼T妹坦言看不起3貼或草菅人命的父母。（圖／T妹臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qZE6llLrk3IGSp1B5gvwKQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU3O2g9ODgx/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/1cf1f2b079e60c6156f1f2f5662b2a6b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqZE6llLrk3IGSp1B5gvwKQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU3O2g9ODgx%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2F1cf1f2b079e60c6156f1f2f5662b2a6b&h=ccbe245f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此文一出引發正反兩派網友爭論，不少人支持T妹的觀點，留言力挺「我覺得講的蠻有道理的，卻被一堆酸民酸」、「我蠻認同妳說的情況，盡量在自己的能力範圍內扶養孩子」、「不論做什麼交通工具，都要以小孩的安全為最優先考量，凡事小心，不要等真的發生狀況了才來後悔」，但也有人表示「住海邊嗎」、「妳小時候也坐過機車出門吧？妳還不是沒死」、「戴安全帽啊，不然乾脆不要出門」、「照妳意思來說，那很多人不應該被生下來，妳的生活這麼理想化」、「去市場買菜也要開車？」<br />\n<br />\n由於一番言論被網友解讀為「羞辱窮人」，讓T妹受到不少攻擊，也令她再度發文，強調很多人騎機車載幼兒是因為安全知識不夠，自己就算在生產前錢被孩子的爸盜領光，現在主要在顧孩子沒什麼收入，也會拜託朋友開車或搭計程車載她的孩子。自己並沒有歧視機車族，只是希望將傷害降到最低，「窮真的不是藉口！安全第一！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CZzcY8OWweOfhBhAs68evQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjE2O2g9NTk4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/b39702d061c05ce80856d29edf68eb7e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCZzcY8OWweOfhBhAs68evQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjE2O2g9NTk4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2Fb39702d061c05ce80856d29edf68eb7e&h=dc2e19a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%A9%9F%E8%BB%8A3%E8%B2%BC%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D-e%E5%A5%B6%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%97%86-%E7%AA%AE%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A9%B2%E7%94%9F-025800188.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%259E%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25BB%258A3%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D-e%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2585%25E5%2597%2586-%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E7%2594%259F-025800188.html&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HHO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=10ab321b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%A9%9F%E8%BB%8A3%E8%B2%BC%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D-e%E5%A5%B6%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%97%86-%E7%AA%AE%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A9%B2%E7%94%9F-025800188.html</a>"},{"pid":"1b6ae94c3747c9c94c683c05074464628499ce1f","tid":1142558,"uid":160807,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「窮人就是不建議生小孩，除非你可以給小孩最基本生活品質」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c5aae49bf4da162a95b94a66b0dd9881e95030","tid":1142558,"uid":123456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母咁多唔關事嘅圖<br />\n台灣傳媒on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"38732820de5ed325181d523b4416eac164230a84","tid":1142558,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c5aae49bf4da162a95b94a66b0dd9881e95030","tid":1142558,"uid":123456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: 